finalEmail.subject: Cherry Hill Properties - Your Preferences
finalEmail.body:
Hi Dan Nik,

Following up on your request, here are a few properties in 08003 that have been on the market for a while, potentially offering room for negotiation, and aiming to be among the 'nicest' in the area.

Property 1: 800 Marlowe Rd, Cherry Hill, NJ, 08003
Price: $599,900, 4 beds, 3 baths, 2056 sqft. 
This property stands out due to its significantly longer time on the market. While it may not be the largest or most expensive, it offers a balance of size and negotiability.

Property 2: 22 Country Walk, Cherry Hill, NJ, 08003
Price: $730,000, 4 beds, 3 baths, 2693 sqft.
This property offers considerable square footage and has also been on the market for a while, suggesting potential for negotiation. It fits the client's location preference but may not be the 'nicest' option.

Property 3: 1869 W Point Dr, Cherry Hill, NJ, 08003
Price: $609,900, 4 beds, 3 baths, 2337 sqft.
This property also offers a decent number of days on the market and meets the bed count criteria. It is located in the preferred zip code, but the 'nicest house' requirement may not be completely satisfied.

Please let me know if you'd like to schedule a viewing for any of these properties or if you have any further questions.
